Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • taAllocation.Entity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Course, Instructor, Lab, Lecture, PredicateReader, TA, Timeslot

    public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    The base class for named things. It implements Comparable so that such objects may be compared using the compareTo(Object) method (useful if putting them in sorted containers).
